FBIS3-12984 "drnes045_l_94006" FBIS-NES-94-045 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Knesset Member Katz Receives Letter From 'Arafat NC0403112694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1000 GMT 4 Mar 94 NC0403112694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Knesset Member Yosi Katz today received a letter from Yasir 'Arafat in which he expresses the hope that all the forces working for peace in Israel will participate in adopting practical measures to block the activities of the settlers, something that will make it possible to quickly implement the Declaration of Principles agreement. Our correspondent Yo'el Nir reports that 'Arafat sent the letter in response to a cable from Knesset Member Katz in which he called on him to demonstrate leadership and overcome those who are trying to torpedo the peace process.
